[Sales Events, Inventory Updates, Competitor Prices] --> Kafka Topics
          ↓
[Kafka Connect Snowflake Sink] --> Snowflake Raw Tables & Streams
          ↓
[Snowflake SQL / Snowpark ML Pricing Models] (real-time analytics + predictions)
          ↓
[Snowflake Tasks & Streams] --> Generates price updates / promotion triggers
          ↓
[Kafka Producer] sends updated prices/promos to Kafka topics
          ↓
[Client Applications] consume pricing updates for frontend / POS
